# perflint
![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/perflint)

pylint extension for performance anti patterns

very much a work-in-progress!

## Installation

```
pip install perflint
```

## Usage

```
pylint your_code/ --load-plugins=perflint
```

